                    <br>
                    More than 35 million stray dogs roam the streets of India, without food, veterinary care or refuge from its often punishing elements. We’re fighting to give them a chance.</p>
                    
                    <p> India’s animal welfare system struggles with a lack of personnel and capital to build infrastructure to help  suffering stray animals. Help us build a network of stray animal rescues, veterinarians, and animal lovers to give these pets-to-be the critical intervention, veterinary care, and ultimately loving home they deserve.</p>
